*bson-3.2.0 (28 Jul 2015)

  28 Jul 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +bson-3.2.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  08 Jun 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> bson-3.0.4.ebuild:
  Update SLOT to allow for a proper dependency in dev-ruby/mongo.

*bson-3.0.4 (08 Jun 2015)

  08 Jun 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +bson-3.0.4.ebuild:
  Version bump for security bug 551496.

  07 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add github to remote-id in metadata.xml

  02 May 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> bson-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Add ruby22.

  09 Mar 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> bson-1.12.0.ebuild:
  Fix SRC_URI and RUBY_S for bug 542600.

*bson-1.12.0 (08 Mar 2015)

  08 Mar 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +bson-1.12.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  05 Jan 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> bson-1.6.2-r1.ebuild,
  bson-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Depend on dev-ruby/rdoc since virtual/ruby-rdoc is a noop these days.

  13 Aug 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> bson-1.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby21 target.

*bson-2.3.0 (16 Jun 2014)

